{"tid":473064,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Quit U 一問","createTime":"2017-11-18T20:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T10:06:45.000Z","uid":151389,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"381d0d3091c1ac4e0ec40e69df252458d739a020","tid":473064,"uid":151389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T20:48:45.000Z","msg":"我知自己攞黎衰架啦,一早已經諗住要quit u考多次jupas但拖到宜家先做野。結果宜家先發現原來出左exam schedule之後係唔比quit。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想問下如果我quit唔到都好,如果我唔再番學,唔交assignment唔去考試既話,會唔會對日後有影響架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係jupas late application要點做?因為如果quit唔到u既話等完sem就會過左jupas deadline<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知我抵架啦,但希望有人答到我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.S.讀poly"},{"pid":"f600640ad15d7151fa002b52404d201f1d6c81c7","tid":473064,"uid":37349,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T23:45:46.000Z","msg":"無事架 jupas late application 都係俾貴小小700左右 3月都仲報到我上年"},{"pid":"5629aade9b257aec174309d23818fc46bd7afd47","tid":473064,"uid":4994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T23:54:57.000Z","msg":"金閃你都quit?"},{"pid":"cc3f2d9799c161eb725980bce42c7928f212d8c0","tid":473064,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T00:08:00.000Z","msg":"無影響 反正你都唔讀"},{"pid":"bfd7f01584c9f3f37c8e4e638265ef328501de32","tid":473064,"uid":151389,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"Check過jupas好似要比多$300，我係驚我唔再番學交功課會比人blacklist整花左個record，影響到下年再報過"},{"pid":"14d0407d63e71229c90833cc1918c910efefbbdc","tid":473064,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:14:30.000Z","msg":"埋大係特別煩，果時quit hd retake dse瘋狂叫我返去搞